        "_account_id": 626,
        "name": "Quentin Bouget",
        "email": "quentin.bouget@cea.fr",
        "username": "bougetq"
      },
      "date": "2017-05-02 07:48:01.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 3: Code-Review-1\n\n(1 comment)\n\nActually we thought about doing this to fix lu-9038 but we concluded it added complexity to a dying api.\n\nIf you really want to clean up kuc (before we remove it) I think it would be better to completely remove the group array => there would be no need for an initialization function, we could simply do\n\n    static LIST_HEAD(kkuc_hsm_group);",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "eccbeed3bb5c16c24abd0e15c09b175c3ffdc405",
      "author": {
        "_account_id": 626,
        "name": "Quentin Bouget",
        "email": "quentin.bouget@cea.fr",
        "username": "bougetq"
      },
      "date": "2017-05-02 14:17:33.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\nThe -1 is more or less just to make sure we can exchange thoughts on this, I mean it as \"I would prefer this not to get merged _right now_\".\n\nIf you think this is the right way to go you have my +1.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "32bccb125a054ead87cb64dbfcbd01d185b12bde",
      "author": {
        "_account_id": 177,
        "name": "John Hammond",
        "email": "jhammond@whamcloud.com",
        "username": "jhammond"
      },
      "date": "2017-05-02 15:56:42.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\nI am fine with removing KUC but I think this is the right fix for now.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 3
    },
    {
      "id": "ccf2d94b1d3a65e77592a80ce72e9e26c7198b52",
